{"tid":1033681,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"新聞透視  走塑偽善","createTime":"2019-02-23T11:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T16:53:02.000Z","uid":38456,"like":165,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"40f97a9f72a466041b47d6cf7f339bca5273da1a","tid":1033681,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:03:51.000Z","msg":"全球「走塑」意識抬頭，香港不少食肆響應推行「走飲管」，卻激起部分市民及網民不滿。為何一個環保的行動，會被視為「擾民」甚至是「偽善」？餐廳想支持環保有何困難？多國將禁用即棄塑膠餐具。本港政府亦稱，預計在今年研究推行相關政策的可能。不過，十年前政府推行膠袋稅，膠袋的使用量最終不跌反升，連帶製造出更多的垃圾。「走塑」會否帶來相同的問題？要在香港移風易俗，需要甚麼條件？"},{"pid":"393f3418860764cf73db32bc2d6095a891e734a2","tid":1033681,"uid":4695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:05:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"917255a5441bf05cfd00acc91f6e48f5426fa632","tid":1033681,"uid":29675,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:06:58.000Z","msg":"$20按金<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c128f7a9edb157855db2cee7a398246b88d43469","tid":1033681,"uid":117837,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:07:19.000Z","msg":"屌鳩環保撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd9f81555aad835703c10740c7521eb1c58576b","tid":1033681,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:08:30.000Z","msg":"靠咩搵食"},{"pid":"da292c8c4f6436d785b90e0c460c77c6a6e20325","tid":1033681,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:09:58.000Z","msg":"咪即係堂食餐具"},{"pid":"aadac4e9d25c125a5ad0d3c5ef09c8e6ad56e73e","tid":1033681,"uid":153136,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:10:06.000Z","msg":"借餐具都算正常環保人士，起碼比直接屌人叫人走餐具嘅環保撚好"},{"pid":"64ec2ec27535c059e8ff8918c901adfc7ea34f49","tid":1033681,"uid":138355,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:10:14.000Z","msg":"記撚住個班搞到全部人食M記冇飲筒嘅撚樣<img src=\"/